short_desc: FRMDATEE2F must not be from date before form was released
full_desc: Q0a. FRMDATEE2F (E2F form date) must not be from date before form was released (2012)

test_name: FTDOTHER compared to FTDOTDOP, FTDOTSER, FTDOTCHO, FTDOTANO
short_desc: If FTDOTHER = 1, one of FTDOTDOP, FTDOTSER, FTDOTCHO, or FTDOTANO must = 1
full_desc: If Q4. FTDOTHER (Other PET or SPECT scans obtained at current or previous evaluation available for sharing?) = 1 (Yes), one of Q4a. FTDOTDOP (Dopaminergic scan available?), Q4b. FTDOTSER (Serotonergic scan available?),  Q4c. FTDOTCHO (Cholinergic scan available?) or Q4d. FTDOTANO (Another kind of scan available?) must = 1 (Yes)
test_logic: FTDOTHER = 1 and FTDOTDOP, FTDOTSER, FTDOTCHO, and FTDOTANO = 0
